                  </hi>. I am servant to Mr. Maldon, in the City-road. I was returning down the Kent-road, about ten o'clock at night, on the 28th of May—there were three boys together—one of them made up to me, and took my reticule from my arm—it contained the property stated—this is it—I I do not know who the person was—he ran down a street.</p>
